{"tid":343701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"怕羞仔買《LoveLive!》攬枕：對她一見鍾情","createTime":"2017-08-01T16:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T07:28:22.000Z","uid":64409,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c9beea26920ab3e9cb9fc1da1624ab9c8e34884","tid":343701,"uid":64409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Myn4_P30jPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMyn4_P30jPU&d=K435MAA8o6XK0r%2BzLFZhTwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=486323ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Myn4_P30jPU</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】動漫節吸引不少市民昨趁周日進場，場內擠滿人，有賣動漫《銀魂》木刀「洞爺湖」的展商三日已賣逾150把。「你好毒呀！」，動漫節亦吸引被標籤為「毒」的宅男宅女離開家門，但所謂「毒」又如何定義？《蘋果》訪問一眾動漫迷訴說心底話，自認「毒」的人多數不介意別人眼光：「如果自己興趣都介意人笑，咁有乜意義？」<br />\n<br />\n一見鍾情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b9e9836c7310e14b0cfe2e2607aafb4ccc509d","tid":343701,"uid":51720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"幾年前係「周X娜抱枕」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77925b5ff6e7d0d463a9ea8383c80648baf6197","tid":343701,"uid":52358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"我愛嗚咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfc46cc48ae28d1af6d257aeefc2116579f00bb","tid":343701,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:59:05.000Z","msg":"個mousepad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463db6b78fdfb2fd3dabf1b53d287ddcfa425051","tid":343701,"uid":48442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:59:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88983f29e566266105403df4e0904fe8be16b0c2","tid":343701,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:02:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76e4d7b7e4d4a5e9f90feb58c8b57597bd7417fa","tid":343701,"uid":55375,"l